f=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"概要","title":"概要","isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>HTML</strong> 的 <code>&lt;style&gt;</code> 元素包含文档的样式信息或者文档的部分内容。默认情况下，该标签的样式信息通常是<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS\">CSS</a>的格式。</p><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"445\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/tabbed/style.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>\n<ul>\n  <li><em><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">内容类别 (en-US)</a></em><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#metadata_content\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">元数据内容 (en-US)</a>，如果指定了 <code>scoped</code> 属性：<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">流内容 (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><em>允许的内容</em>与 <code>type</code> 属性相匹配的文本内容，也就是 <code>text/css</code></li>\n  <li><em>标签忽略</em> 不允许，开始标签和结束标签都不能省略。</li>\n  <li><em>允许的父元素</em> 任意接受<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#metadata_content\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">元数据内容 (en-US)</a>的元素</li>\n  <li>_Permitted ARIA roles_None</li>\n  <li><em>DOM 接口</em> <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLStyleElement\"><code>HTMLStyleElement</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<p>该元素包含所有<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\">全局属性</a>。</p>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"type\"><a id=\"attr-type\" href=\"#attr-type\"><b><code>type</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>该属性以 MIME 类型（不应该指定字符集）定义样式语言。如果该属性未指定，则默认为 <code>text/css</code>。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"media\"><a id=\"attr-media\" href=\"#attr-media\"><b><code>media</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>该属性规定该样式适用于哪个媒体。属性的取值<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Media_Queries/Using_media_queries\">CSS 媒体查询</a>，默认值为 <code>all</code>。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"nonce\"><a id=\"attr-nonce\" href=\"#attr-nonce\"><b><code>nonce</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>一种加密的随机数（一次使用的数字），用于在<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Content-Security-Policy/style-src\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">style-src Content-Security-Policy (en-US)</a>中将内联样式列入白名单。 服务器每次发送策略时都必须生成一个唯一的随机数值。 提供一个无法猜测的随机数非常重要，因为绕开资源策略是微不足道的。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"title\"><a id=\"attr-title\" href=\"#attr-title\"><b><code>title</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>指定可选的样式表。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"已淘汰属性","title":"已淘汰属性","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"scoped\"><a id=\"attr-scoped\" href=\"#attr-scoped\"><b><code>scoped</code></b></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>此属性指定样式仅适用于其父项和子项的元素。</p>\n    <div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n      <p><strong>备注：</strong> 以后可能会根据<a href=\"https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/3547\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/3547</a>重新引入此属性。 如果要立即使用该属性，则可以使用<a href=\"https://github.com/samthor/scoped\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">polyfill</a>。</p>\n    </div>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"一个简单的样式表","title":"一个简单的样式表","isH3":true,"content":"<p>在下面的例子中，我们将简单的样式应用到文档中：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">doctype</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n    <span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>This is my paragraph.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"一个简单的样式表\" id=\"frame_a_simple_stylesheet\" width=\"100%\" height=\"60\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style/_sample_.a_simple_stylesheet.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"多种样式元素","title":"多种样式元素","isH3":true,"content":"<p>在这个例子中包含两种样式 <code>&lt;style&gt;</code> 元素</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">doctype</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n    <span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> white<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> blue<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 5px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1px solid black<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n    <span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> blue<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> yellow<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>This is my paragraph.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"多种样式元素\" id=\"frame_multiple_style_elements\" width=\"100%\" height=\"60\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style/_sample_.multiple_style_elements.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"包含媒体_media_选择","title":"包含媒体 (media) 选择","isH3":true,"content":"<p>这个例子根据前一个例子构建，在第二个 <code>&lt;style&gt;</code> 中，视图宽度小于 500px 时生效</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">doctype</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n    <span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> white<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> blue<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 5px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1px solid black<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">media</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>all and (max-width: 500px)<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n    <span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> blue<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> yellow<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>This is my paragraph.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"包含媒体 (media) 选择\" id=\"frame_including_a_media_query\" width=\"100%\" height=\"60\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style/_sample_.including_a_media_query.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/semantics.html#the-style-element","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"html.elements.style"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"html.elements.style","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"查看更多","title":"查看更多","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/link\"><code>&lt;link&gt;</code></a>元素允许使用外部的样式表。</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Alternative_style_sheets\">Alternative Style Sheets</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"概要","id":"概要"},{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"查看更多","id":"查看更多"}],"summary":"HTML 的 <style> 元素包含文档的样式信息或者文档的部分内容。默认情况下，该标签的样式信息通常是CSS的格式。","popularity":0.0024,"modified":"202